    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract interface for objects that are updated (ticked) every frame. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implementors receive regular tick callbacks from the engine with the elapsed time since the last update. Implementations should keep ticks fast and avoid long blocking operations. </para>
